From: Marcin FM <marcin@lgic.pl>
Subject: [PATCH] Use Fedora-compatible SHA-1 build IDs

RPM requires build IDs long enough for its build-id link hierarchy. Chromium's
LLD fast build ID is only eight bytes, so use the SHA-1 form for this Fedora
build.

--- a/build/config/compiler/BUILD.gn
+++ b/build/config/compiler/BUILD.gn
@@ -515 +515 @@
-        ldflags += [ "-Wl,--build-id=fast" ]
+        ldflags += [ "-Wl,--build-id=sha1" ]
